Earn Up To 4,000 Bonus Miles On Our New Nonstop Service From 
New York To London/Stansted

Our new service from New York/Newark to London/Stansted begins* May 1, 2001.
And, from May 1 through July 1, 2001, flights to London/Stansted earn you 
2,000 bonus miles each way. That's in addition to the actual miles flown. 
Stansted Airport is convenient for travelers going to central London, Canary
Wharf and Docklands, as well as regional cities like Cambridge. So book your 
tickets today at www.continental.com.

* Service is subject to government approval.


Earn 15,000 OnePassc Bonus Miles With CSFBdirect

We're excited to announce another great opportunity to earn major bonus miles 
with a OnePass partner. You will receive 15,000 OnePass bonus miles when you 
open a new CSFBdirect account with a minimum deposit or transfer of 
$5,000. CSFBdirect is the online investment firm that combines the experience
and resources of DLJdirect and Credit Suisse First Boston.  Let your 
investments put you that much closer to your next free ticket. To learn more 
about this excellent opportunity visit www.csfbdirect.com/ilikemiles


Discount on Camp Inventionc For OnePass Members

Continental Airlines, the Official Airline of The National Inventors Hall of
Fame, is pleased to offer Continental OnePass members a special registration 
rate on NIHF's premier education program, Camp Invention. This nationally 
recognized science and creativity day camp for children entering grades 2-6 
takes a unique hands-on approach to learning. OnePass members receive a 
discount rate of $160 through May 31 simply by providing their OnePass number 
when registering. Check out the camp website at www.invent.org for camp dates 
and locations nearest you or call 1.800.968.4332 to register for Camp 
Invention 2001.



